creator: William le Queux
description:
LibriVox recording of Stolen Souls by William le Queux.
Read in English by Alan Winterrowd; Anna Simon; Annapurna; bala; Christine Dufour; Etel Buss; John O; Lee Smalley; Lynne Thompson; Mary in Arkansas; ToddHW
This is a collection of 14 of William le Queux' best mystery stories. (Summary by Carolin)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
Standard or slim CD Case Insert available for this recording.

M4B format available
subject: librivox; audiobooks;
title: Stolen Souls

reviews.reviewbody: This collection has a wonderful title. The stories, however, are surprisingly blah. The readers try hard, but the ending of each of these is blah. The best some of these can do is provide a healthy dose of circa 1900 political atmosphere.
